<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/oct/10/">&#x27a0;</a> October 10, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="open_source_mad" >

        
        <a name="002992"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.desktoplinux.com/news/NS9068065177.html">Open Source madness!</a></h4>

        

        <p>Good commentary of the unpleasantness that&#8217;s about to unfold with this Firefox/Iceweasel fork.  The two new &#8220;features&#8221; which will now ship with Debian, Ubuntu, et al are just the tip of an iceberg of confusion and incompatibility.</p>

