<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/mar/19/">&#x27a0;</a> March 19, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="dariks_boot_and_nuke" >

        
        <a name="002326"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://dban.sourceforge.net/">Darik&#39;s Boot and Nuke</a></h4>

        

        <p>Bootdisk that fits on a 1.44Mb floppy which securely nukes every scrap of data off of hard drives.  Handy to have if you&#8217;re about to sell an old computer.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
