<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/dec/28/">&#x27a0;</a> December 28, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="truecrypt_free_opensource_onth" >

        
        <a name="002186"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.truecrypt.org/">TrueCrypt - Free Open-Source On-The-Fly Disk Encryption Software for Windows XP/2000 and Linux</a></h4>

        

        <p>Open-source whole-disk encryption package for Windows.  Perfect for keeping your USB keychain drive safe from prying eyes.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
